de.iabg.mesh.io
Class NastranBulkDataReader

java.lang.Object
  java.io.Reader
      java.io.InputStreamReader
          java.io.FileReader
              de.iabg.mesh.io.NastranBulkDataReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
GeometryReader, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.Readable
public class NastranBulkDataReader
extends java.io.FileReader
implements GeometryReader

This implementation of GeometryReader parses a Nastran file containing geometry data, namely nodes, edges, triangles, and quadrilaterals. Refer to GeometryReader class API for more details. The Nastran file can come in three formats, called free, large, and small. This parser is designed to handle each format for every line. Refer to the latest version of the MSC.Nastran Quick Reference Guide for more information for the file format.

Version:
September 13, 2008
Author:
Adam C. Dick, BSE
